  <h3>About Us</h3>
  <p>
    Slaymaker Cellars is a small
    <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benefit_corporation" target="_blank">Benefit Corporation</a>
    located in Idaho Springs, CO. We make mead from all Colorado ingredients. We are in the process of setting up
    an employee ownership program.
  </p>
  <p>
    Mead is wine made from honey. We have a few varieties available, including pure honey traditional mead, spiced mead,
    and a collection of fruit meads. It is our belief that mead is every bit as versatile a beverage as wine. Our mead
    is available in Central Colorado and we can ship direct to customer in 42 states.
  </p>
  <p>
    Slaymaker Cellars currently has 3 employees and is seeing good, sustainable growth. We are currently
    building our brand in order to justify the expense of a tasting room and retail location. </p>
  <p>

  </p>

